// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1090 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 16f6bcfe-8871-5e4a-8102-7e9a5f52542d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:8* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:16.04-ESM*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
